race.description: Become A Brc Member Maiden Plate
race.comment: MEDITERRA (11) brings NSW formlines to the table and should find this assignment a touch easier. Only needs to some luck navigating from the sticky draw to be featuring in the finish. WILIAMTHECONQUEROR (1) resumes here but has tuned up for this with a recent trial win and is drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley. Can run a race while fresh. MEADOWBROOK (7) has placed two from two around this circuit and draws nicely in gate three. Worth including in calculations. The well-related TSZYUYA (8) (half to G2 winner Amazonian Lass) returns from a lay-off. Recent trial winner at Doomben. Opened last campaign with a second at this track over 1200m. Include.
